Nicolas Mirzayantz



Mr. Nicolas Mirzayantz is Group President-Fragrances at International Flavors & Fragrances, Inc. He is on the Board of Directors at The Fragrance Foundation, Fragrance Materials Association of the United States, and International Fragrance Association.
He received his graduate degree from Pantheon-Assas University.



