Nicolas Mirzayantz
Group President, Fragrances, International Flavors & Fragrances Inc. (IFF)


International Executive Programme, INSEAD. 1986-87, Deputy Trade Commissioner, French Embassy, Nicaragua. Since 1988, with International Flavors & Fragrances; formerly, Regional Manager, North America and General Manager, France; currently, Group President, Fragrances; President, Laboratoire Monique Remy Naturals; Leader, Global Sustainability Initiatives. Vice-Chair, Industry Advisory Board, Master's Programme, Fashion Institute of Technology. Member of the Board, International Fragrance Association. Member of the Board of Governors, We Are Family Foundation. Recipient of industry awards including Beyond Beauty for OCD Research.
















