Group President Fragrance of Internationa Flavors & Fragranc (NYSE:IFF), Mirzayantz Nicolas, sells 1,233 shares worth $164,926
According to Internationa Flavors & Fragranc's most recent Form 4 filing with the SEC dated Jul 18 11:39 AM, company Group President Fragrance, Mirzayantz Nicolas disclosed selling 1,233 shares at a cost of $133.76. At the time of this transaction (Jul 17), this trade was worth $164,926 in total. As of Jul 17, Mirzayantz Nicolas now owns 46,274 shares in total worth about $6,233,570.54. 
